### Start a new order processing saga
POST http://localhost:7071/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerId": "customer123",
  "productId": "product456",
  "quantity": 5,
  "amount": 100.00
}

### Check the status of an order processing saga
# Replace {instanceId} with the actual ID returned from the start request
GET http://localhost:7071/api/orders/{instanceId}

### Terminate an order processing saga
# Replace {instanceId} with the actual ID you want to terminate
POST http://localhost:7071/api/orders/{instanceId}/terminate

### Note about monitoring
# When using Azurite, there's no built-in dashboard like with Durable Task Scheduler
# Use Azure Storage Explorer to view the Azure Storage contents and monitor orchestrations
